    <string name="texto_manual_usuario_titulo">User Manual</string>
    <string name="texto_manual_usuario">
        Welcome to the official THE RING PRIVATE app.\n\n
        1. REGISTRATION AND LOGIN\n
        To access, you must be registered with your ID and email. If you forget your password, you can recover it from the home screen.\n\n
        2. QR CODE\n
        On the home screen, you have a personal QR code. This code is your identification to access the club. Scan it at the reception.\n\n
        3. NOTIFICATIONS\n
        Stay up to date with all events and special meetings in the notifications section.\n\n
        4. PROFILE AND SETTINGS\n
        You can customize your nickname in the profile and change the language or appearance (dark/light mode) in the settings.\n\n
        5. RULES\n
        It is mandatory to comply with the club rules, which you can consult at any time in the corresponding section.\n\n
        6. SECURITY\n
        You can permanently delete your account from the settings if you wish.
    </string>
